    "title":"Iterate Through a Range",
    "content":[
      "The for loop in Kotlin iterates through anything that provides an iterator.",
      "Here, the loop iterates through the range and prints individual item."
     ],
    "code": [
      "fun main(args: Array<String>) {",
      "    for (i in 1..5) {",
      "        println(i)",
      "    }",
      "}"
